{
  "title": "Vim更改行号颜色",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><br></div><div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial;\"><div id=\"isForwardContent\"><div style=\"line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\">更改行号颜色</span></div><span style=\"font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><div><span style=\"line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><br></span></div>为了改变行号的颜色，可以用highlight命令设置：默认是黄色的yellow&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\">:hi linenr ctermfg=lightcyan&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\">或者颜色深点：&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\">:hi linenr ctermfg=darkblue &nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 255);\">此处不用加分号</span>(eg:darkred,lightgreen........)</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\">hi LineNr guibg=darkgrey ctermbg=darkgrey guifg=white ctermfg=grey&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><div class=\"postbody\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\">行号前的空格可以用&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">set nuw=1</div><div><br></div><span style=\"font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\">在/usr/share/vim/vim71/colors/可以看到各种颜色方案。&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div class=\"postbody\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><br></div><div style=\"line-height: 1.7;\"><br></div><div style=\"line-height: 1.7;\"><br></div><div style=\"line-height: 1.7;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 0);\">以下设置不是更改行号颜色,是更改控制台其他方面颜色:</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 244, 239);\"><div><br></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">输入：&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">:highlight&nbsp;LineNr&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">LineNr&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;xxx&nbsp;term=underline&nbsp;ctermfg=14&nbsp;guifg=yellow&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">即可看到当前行号显示状态的设置情况，&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">根据你的需要重新修改即可，&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">例如：&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">:highlight&nbsp;LineNr&nbsp;guifg=green&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">具体情况参看：&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">:help&nbsp;highlight&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\"></div></div></div><br><br><span title=\"neteasefooter\"><span id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 10px 5px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px;\">来自网易手机号码邮箱<a id=\"mobile_set\" sys=\"1\" log=\"1\" logid=\"free_sms_20120504\" href=\"http://shouji.163.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">了解更多</a></div></div></span></span></div></div><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><span title=\"neteasefooter\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 